text: Jaroslav Bílek (born 16 March 1971) is a Czech former cyclist. He competed in the team time trial at the 1992 Summer Olympics. He also won the Peace Race in 1993. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Czechoslovakia Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from Vimperk
